            <title>[LU-9729] missing mutex unlock in  lnet_dyn_add_net()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9729</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;lnet_dyn_add_net() returns without unlocking the mutex. This API is only for backwards compatibility. MR interface should be calling lnet_dyn_add_ni()&lt;/p&gt;</description>
